(391, 1, '2015-01-08 11:34:36', '2015-01-08 11:34:36', '<div class="main_heading full_width">\n        <h1 class="red_color ">Advance Opportunities for All</h1>\n        <div class="main_headingBorder"></div>\n      </div>\n     <div class="plan_inner_part full_width top_margin">\n          <h2 class="red_color btm_padding1">Quality Neighborhoods and Housing for All</h2>\n     <p class="btm_padding">Goal:   Ensure safe and proud neighborhoods and quality affordable housing for all.\nMayor Kristen Brown’s plan revitalizes and strengthens our neighborhoods and business corridors by the elimination of blight and through rehabilitation and redevelopment, including the development of quality affordable housing.</p>\n<img src="http://localhost/brown-for-columbus/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Opportunities.png" alt="Opportunities" width="998" height="374" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-287" />\n     </div>\n     <div class="inner_text_container full_width top_margin">\n<ul>\n<li>Revitalize and Redevelop State Street Corridor according to our plan.</li>\n<li>Revitalize our neighborhoods through infrastructure improvements, stronger property maintenance codes, code enforcement, blight elimination programs, neighborhood cleanups and incentives for private investment in targeted revitalization areas.\n</li>\n<li>Increase the number of affordable housing units in our community through public-private partnerships.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>', 'Advance Opportunities for All', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '270-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-01-08 11:34:36', '2015-01-08 11:34:36', '', 270, 'http://localhost/brown-for-columbus/270-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(392, 1, '2015-01-08 11:34:38', '2015-01-08 11:34:38', '<div class="main_heading full_width">\r\n        <h1 class="red_color ">Advance Opportunities for All</h1>\r\n        <div class="main_headingBorder"></div>\r\n      </div>\r\n     <div class="plan_inner_part full_width top_margin">\r\n          <h2 class="red_color btm_padding1">Quality Neighborhoods and Housing for All</h2>\r\n     <p class="btm_padding">Goal:   Ensure safe and proud neighborhoods and quality affordable housing for all.\r\nMayor Kristen Brown’s plan revitalizes and strengthens our neighborhoods and business corridors by the elimination of blight and through rehabilitation and redevelopment, including the development of quality affordable housing.</p>\r\n<img src="http://localhost/brown-for-columbus/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Opportunities.png" alt="Opportunities" width="998" height="374" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-287" />\r\n     </div>\r\n     <div class="inner_text_container full_width top_margin">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Revitalize and Redevelop State Street Corridor according to our plan.</li>\r\n<li>Revitalize our neighborhoods through infrastructure improvements, stronger property maintenance codes, code enforcement, blight elimination programs, neighborhood cleanups and incentives for private investment in targeted revitalization areas.\r\n</li>\r\n<li>Increase the number of affordable housing units in our community through public-private partnerships.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>', 'Advance Opportunities for All', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '270-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-01-08 11:34:38', '2015-01-08 11:34:38', '', 270, 'http://localhost/brown-for-columbus/270-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(393, 1, '2015-01-08 11:35:17', '2015-01-08 11:35:17', '      <div class="plan_inner_part full_width">\r\n        <p class="blue_color_normal">We are one of the safest communities in the country. However, when it comes to our personal safety and the protection of our property, there will always be room for improvement. A healthy community includes living healthy lifestyles and living in an </p>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div class="community_part full_width ">\r\n        <div class="community_leftPart">\r\n          <p class="blue_color_normal">environmentally safe community.</p>\r\n          <p class="top_padding blue_color_normal">Mayor Kristen Brown’s goals for a safe and healthy community include:</p>\r\n          <h2 class="red_color btm_padding1">Safest Community</h2>\r\n          <p class=" btm_padding1">Goal:  Be the safest city of our size in the country.</p>\r\n          <p class=" btm_padding1">Mayor Kristen Brown’s plan calls for sustaining and advancing your and your family’s safety as her highest priority.</p>\r\n          <p >Thankfully, our violent crime is in the lowest ten percent of the nation.  However, dangerous drugs are prevalent in our community.  Not only does drug abuse destroy the lives of users and families, it is fueling a property crime rate that is unacceptably high.  Mayor Brown’s priority is to:</p>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div class="img_container top_margin"><img src="http://localhost/brown-for-columbus/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/health.png" alt="health" width="441" height="320" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-284" /></div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div class="inner_text_container full_width top_margin ">\r\n        <ul>\r\n          <li>Stem the tide of dangerous drugs into our community and cut our property crime rate by continuing to accelerate our narcotics investigations and community policing efforts and by leveraging technology as a force multiplier.</li>\r\n        </ul>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div class="community_btmPart full_width ">\r\n        <div class="inner_text_container full_width ">\r\n          <h2>Healthy Community</h2>\r\n          <p class="top_padding" >Goal:  Radically improve the health and wellness of our residents through healthy behaviors, healthy lifestyles and access to healthcare.</p>\r\n          <p class="top_padding" >Obesity, substance abuse and mental illness remain the most vexing health problems facing us today.  We’re making great progress on these fronts but we have much more work to do.</p>\r\n          <p class="top_padding btm_padding1" >Mayor Kristen Brown’s plan ensures that the community collectively supports both mental and physical wellness. </p>\r\n          <ul>\r\n            <li>Cut the demand for drugs in our community through significantly greater leadership and resources directed toward prevention and treatment of substance abuse and mental health disorders.  Cutting the supply of drugs will remain a tremendous challenge until we seriously address the demand for drugs in our community.</li>\r\n            <li>Build People Bridges, dedicated bike and pedestrian bridges, to make important and safe People Trail connections over our rivers, busy streets and railroad tracks, including the riverfront of the Pump House property, over Lindsey into downtown at the 3rd Street Bridge and over Haw Creek and Central near 3rd Street. </li>\r\n            <li>Form a public-private partnership to develop an indoor athletic training facility on the airport’s property for use by our local sports teams, including soccer, football and other field sports teams.</li>            \r\n          </ul>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </div>', 'Advance the Safety and Health of Our Community', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '297-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-01-08 11:35:17', '2015-01-08 11:35:17', '', 297, 'http://localhost/brown-for-columbus/297-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(394, 1, '2015-01-08 11:35:34', '2015-01-08 11:35:34', '<div class="main_heading full_width">\r\n<h1 class="red_color ">Good Government Values</h1>\r\n        <div class="main_headingBorder"></div>\r\n      </div>\r\n     <div class="plan_inner_part full_width top_margin">\r\n     <p class="btm_padding blue_color_normal">Mayor Kristen Brown has ushered in a new era of good government and led the development a set of core values for City officials and employees that embody the principles of good government.\r\nOur values are important because they provide the foundation for how we pursue our vision.  How we get there is every bit as important as getting there.</p><span><a href="http://localhost/brown-for-columbus/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/value.png"><img src="http://localhost/brown-for-columbus/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/value.png" alt="value" width="1001" height="320" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-277" /></a></span>\r\n     </div><div class="inner_value full_width top_margin">    \r\n<ul>\r\n<li><h2>INTEGRITY WITHOUT COMPROMISE</h2></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class="btm_padding">We are honest and ethical in all we say and do. We honor our word and keep our commitments. </p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><h2>PROFESSIONALISM</h2></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class="btm_padding">We treat every person with respect, dignity and equity. We are positive, courteous, conscientious and businesslike in all of our actions.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><h2>CUSTOMER FIRST</h2></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class="btm_padding">We put the needs of our customers, the people of Columbus, at the heart of everything we do. We strive to be responsive and exceed their expectations at all times. </p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><h2>PEOPLE WORKING TOGETHER</h2></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class="btm_padding">We care deeply about our people and recognize them as our most valuable asset. We work as a team across all boundaries.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><h2>OPENNESS</h2></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class="btm_padding">We are receptive and accessible and our work is transparent. </p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><h2>ACCOUNTABILITY</h2></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class="btm_padding">We take responsibility for our actions and for delivering results.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><h2>FISCAL RESPONSIBILITY</h2></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class="btm_padding">We get the most from the taxpayer’s dollar. We live within our means. We are fiscally very solid.</p>\r\n\r\n</div></div>\r\n', 'Good Government Values', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '273-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-01-08 11:35:34', '2015-01-08 11:35:34', '', 273, 'http://localhost/brown-for-columbus/273-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(395, 1, '2015-01-13 04:57:35', '2015-01-13 04:57:35', '<div class="main_heading full_width">\n  <h1 class="red_color ">Advance the Safety and Health of Our Community</h1>\n  <div class="main_headingBorder"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="plan_text_container full_width top_margin">\n        <p class="blue_color_normal btm_padding1" >We are one of the safest communities in the country. However, when it comes to our personal safety and the protection of our property, there will always be room for improvement. A healthy community includes living healthy lifestyles and living in an environmentally safe community.</p>          \n          <h2 class="red_color btm_padding1" >Safest Community</h2>\n          <p class=" btm_padding1 blue_color_normal">Goal: Be the safest city of our size in the country.</p>\n          <p class=" btm_padding1 blue_color_normal">Mayor Kristen Brown’s plan calls for sustaining and advancing your and your family’s safety as her highest priority.</p>\n          <p class=" blue_color_normal">Thankfully, our violent crime is in the lowest ten percent of the nation.  However, dangerous drugs are prevalent in our community.  Not only does drug abuse destroy the lives of users and families, it is fueling a property crime rate that is unacceptably high.  Mayor Brown’s priority is to:</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class="nner_text_container full_width top_margin"></div>     \n      <div class="inner_text_container full_width top_margin ">\n        <ul>\n          <li>Stem the tide of dangerous drugs into our community and cut our property crime rate by continuing to accelerate our narcotics investigations and community policing efforts and by leveraging technology as a force multiplier.</li>\n        </ul>\n      </div>\n      <div class="community_btmPart full_width ">\n        <div class="inner_text_container full_width ">\n          <h2>Healthy Community</h2>\n          <p class="top_padding" ><span class="bold_color1">Goal:</span>  Radically improve the health and wellness of our residents through healthy behaviors, healthy lifestyles and access to healthcare.</p>\n          <p class="top_padding" >Obesity, substance abuse and mental illness remain the most vexing health problems facing us today.  We’re making great progress on these fronts but we have much more work to do.</p>\n          <p class="top_padding btm_padding1" >Mayor Kristen Brown’s plan ensures that the community collectively supports both mental and physical wellness. </p>\n          <ul>\n            <li>Cut the demand for drugs in our community through significantly greater leadership and resources directed toward prevention and treatment of substance abuse and mental health disorders.  Cutting the supply of drugs will remain a tremendous challenge until we seriously address the demand for drugs in our community.</li>\n            <li>Build People Bridges, dedicated bike and pedestrian bridges, to make important and safe People Trail connections over our rivers, busy streets and railroad tracks, including the riverfront of the Pump House property, over Lindsey into downtown at the 3rd Street Bridge and over Haw Creek and Central near 3rd Street. </li>\n            <li>Form a public-private partnership to develop an indoor athletic training facility on the airport’s property for use by our local sports teams, including soccer, football and other field sports teams.</li>            \n          </ul>\n        </div>\n      </div>', 'Advance the Safety and Health of Our Community', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '297-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-01-13 04:57:35', '2015-01-13 04:57:35', '', 297, 'http://localhost/brown-for-columbus/297-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
