 High School in 1982. She graduated from Brown University with a B.A., magna cum laude, in 1986 and from Harvard University with an M.B.A in 1993.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n', 'About Kristen', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '14-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-01-10 06:59:07', '2015-01-10 06:59:07', '', 14, 'http://localhost/brown-for-columbus/14-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
